column1: #Text=There 's more than one place called Santa Cruz :
#Text=Santa Cruz ( Argentina ) - a province in the Patagonia ( Argentina ) region
#Text=Santa Cruz ( department , Bolivia ) - Bolivia 's largest department
#Text=Santa Cruz ( city , Bolivia ) - capital city of Santa Cruz ( department , Bolivia )
#Text=Santa Cruz do Rio Pardo , São Paulo
#Text=Santa Cruz do Sul , Rio Grande do Sul
#Text=( Isla Santa Cruz , or Indefatigable Island ) - one of the Galapagos Islands
#Text=Santa Cruz ( Laguna ) - A town in Laguna
#Text=Santa Cruz ( Philippines ) - A city in Marinduque
#Text=Santa Cruz ( Manila ) - A district of Manila .
#Text=Santa Cruz ( Portugal ) - a city on Madeira Island , in the Madeira archipelago
#Text=Santa Cruz Islands - an archipelago forming part of the Solomon Islands
#Text=Santa Cruz de Tenerife - capital city of the island of Tenerife , and joint capital ( with Las Palmas de Gran Canaria ) of the Canary Islands
#Text=Santa Cruz de La Palma - largest city of the island of La Palma
#Text=Santa Cruz ( California ) - a city in Santa Cruz County , in the Bay Area region of California
#Text=Santa Cruz ( New Mexico ) - a town in Santa Fe County , North Central New Mexico
#Text=a town in the South Texas Plains , Texas
#Text=Santa Cruz County ( Arizona ) - in South Central Arizona
#Text=Santa Cruz County ( California ) - in the Bay Area region of California
#Text=Santa Cruz Island - the largest of the five islands that make up the Channel Islands National Park , in Southern California
#Text=Santa Cruz Mountains - a mountain range in central California
